{"tid":1616451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武文宣] [敵退我追] 就大你兩個《緊急法》","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:34.000Z","uid":89898,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"37ed617c258e7d4122b85cf3a99650d4926fc3b3","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"嗱即是咁，用《緊急法》立《蒙面法》係步險棋，當中主要問題係喺前者，好多手足都講咗。<br />\n<br />\n有《蒙面法》的確對好多法律體制完善啲嘅國家而言並非大事，但係《緊急法》係代表港共政權正式宣佈實行獨裁政府，今日可以閂埋門個幾鐘出條《蒙面法》，聽日就可以有《禁集會法》《禁連登法》《送中法》《國安法》《習大大是最好法》《理鳩你奧美日英俄德意法》。<br />\n<br />\n個幾鐘前就有消息話，行會打算押後公佈日期，呢個值得諗諗。唔知港共係真係基於法律基礎問題立唔到、定低估咗香港人淨係會focus《蒙面法》唔理《緊急法》呢個大boss、定已經有商家佬唔妥動用《緊急法》、定純粹吹風等大家放軟手腳，點都好總之而家就敵退，咁就係時候我追。<br />\n<br />\n有位巴打嘅呢個post《【提早萬聖節】10月5日全民蒙面遊行，用創意爭取國際關注緊急法》(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1616163/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1616163/page/1?post=1</a>) 提議嘅方式正正係啲外國人期待嘅gimmick嘢，可以一戰搏畫面，但係同時口號呀文宣banner嗰啲係主力介紹《緊急法》。純粹拋磚引玉：「今日禁我蒙面，聽日將你送中」「Mask ban today, Xiang Gang tomorrow」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位巴打嘅《我認為大家聽日根本唔需要去添馬圍佢》都好正 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1616271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1616271/page/1</a>)。有冇熟外國戰線嘅手足，睇吓有冇機email又好twitter comment又好登報又好，直接同外國投資者介紹呢條咁反資本主義嘅法律？<br />\n<br />\n港共要玩《緊急法》呀嘛，我地就大大聲用國際社會講你要用《緊急法》，等全球喺香港嘅投資者都知你玩《緊急法》。記住重點係《緊急法》，呢條先係攬炒大法，因為會直接損害香港營商環境；而《蒙面法》對外迴響就間接好多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：</span></strong></span>唔好諗住押後公佈就放軟手腳，亦唔好淨係執著《蒙面法》。《緊急法》就係攬炒，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港共放風要攬炒，我地就大佢兩個攬炒</span></strong></span>，同佢show hand睇吓邊個淆先，主動出擊斷佢老母後路。"},{"pid":"bf3e01193432278d5bb6b6a563495f7e59ad237b","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">敵退我追</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf557fa887a1f5e323e5a6df4e9676f80f138c69","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大你兩個緊急法</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebdf4e35410b5396eba3529e986ab5f428d63b0","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒吖嗱</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d5a8652e334106b12011b32ca55410574a8ddf","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好淆呀垃圾</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11078c52ac99a8d63d7d033704a0d64b04791523","tid":1616451,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c563cd9ffac8fb685cb889563d7470776a6b7f1","tid":1616451,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"屌啲hyperlink永遠都痴埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2740ba2437e28076f1835ae67237f924a95dc6","tid":1616451,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c466